{"title":"春雨潇潇","authors":["徐琏"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":4,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨潇潇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海师范学院  徐琏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，春雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如碎银般闪亮的春雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如珍珠般宝贵的春雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正轻盈、欢快地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扑进大地母亲温热的怀里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤劳而纯朴的农人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓一把金灿灿的种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只扬一扬手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那绿色的生命便降落于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥沃、褐色的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那金色的希望便升腾于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"善良、宽舒的心底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当村头的小河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在作一年一度的冬眠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当迎春的爆竹喜洋洋地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在空中蹦跳着喘气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他就扳着农人特有的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粗大的手指"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"计算着播种的时日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厚厚的嘴唇轻轻嚅动着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眉宇间流露出甜甜的焦急"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小草已萌动了玉色的胚芽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨柳刚透出了黄色的笑意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，春雨潇潇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散布着绿色的生命，金色的希"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冀……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}